node.title: World Cup qualifier live: Socceroos face China as road to Qatar continues
node.alt: A Socceroos player controls the ball while playing against Oman in a FIFA World Cup qualifier.
node.description: Coming off a scoreless draw against Saudi Arabia, the Socceroos play China on neutral territory in Sharjah, as they chase a berth in next year's FIFA World Cup. Follow our ScoreCentre.
